snippet.title: I Ate At 7-Elevens Across Asia
snippet.description:
Thanks again to Rosetta Stone for sponsoring this video!! Start your language journey today at https://partners.rosettastone.com/safiyanygaard for an exclusive discount of over 60% off an unlimited lifetime language subscription!! 🍡

#rosettastone #rosettastonepartner 

HELLO FRIENDS!! And welcome to the 7-Eleven haul of my dreams!! Now, on our previous trips to East Asia, we definitely noticed the prevalence of 7-Elevens pretty much everywhere - and not only were we surprised by how widespread and popular they were - we quickly realized, they had a lot of pretty awesome stuff we don’t have in the states - like, baos, teas, sandos, noodles, iced coffees, unique chip flavors, pancake sandwiches, corn ice cream - and more!! And once we returned - I started to notice how many people online were also going to international 7-Elevens and doing snack hauls - and I realized - this is a convenience store movement!! 

So on our travels over the past year, we’ve collected 7-Eleven tours and hauls in each country we visited - Singapore, Malaysia, and Japan… to try out some viral snacks, and generally compare them, but also mostly just to feast! Which country’s 7-Eleven should we visit next? 

Also, there is some controversy around birds nest products that we weren't aware of before filming, our apologies. If you'd like to know more, here are a couple of links to some more information -

https://www.businessinsider.com/birds-nest-delicacy-asia-price-farming-benefits-2021-3
https://tableagent.com/article/birds-nest-soup-savory-delicacy-or-gourmet-cruelty/
https://naturalnest.com/blogs/news/ethics-of-harvesting-bird-nests-the-what-you-need-to-know?srsltid=AfmBOorW9H0KXEyJVxYXWB6E-6dxs2C64u3zRrl0MTJ3y9cYnDNyG5M4

es-US.title: Comí en 7-Elevens en toda Asia
es-US.description:
¡Gracias de nuevo a Rosetta Stone por patrocinar este video! ¡Comienza tu viaje de idiomas hoy mismo en https://partners.rosettastone.com/safiyanygaard y obtén un descuento exclusivo de más del 60% en una suscripción de idiomas ilimitada de por vida! 🍡

#rosettastone #rosettastonepartner

¡HOLA AMIGOS! ¡Bienvenidos a la compra de 7-Eleven de mis sueños! En nuestros viajes anteriores al Este de Asia, notamos la abundancia de 7-Elevens en casi todas partes. No solo nos sorprendió su popularidad, sino que enseguida nos dimos cuenta de que tenían muchísimas cosas increíbles que no tenemos en Estados Unidos, como baos, tés, sándwiches, fideos, café helado, sabores únicos de papas fritas, sándwiches de panqueques, helado de maíz, ¡y mucho más! Y al regresar, empecé a notar cuánta gente en línea también iba a 7-Elevens internacionales y compraba bocadillos, y me di cuenta de que ¡esto es un fenómeno de tiendas de conveniencia!

Así que, durante nuestros viajes del último año, recopilamos tours y compras de 7-Eleven en cada país que visitamos: Singapur, Malasia y Japón… para probar algunos snacks virales y compararlos, ¡pero también para darnos un festín! ¿Qué 7-Eleven de qué país deberíamos visitar próximamente?

Además, hay cierta controversia sobre los productos de nido de pájaro que desconocíamos antes de grabar. Disculpen las molestias. Si quieres saber más, aquí tienes un par de enlaces:

de-DE.title: Ich habe in ganz Asien bei 7-Eleven gegessen
de-DE.description:
Nochmals vielen Dank an Rosetta Stone für das Sponsoring dieses Videos! Starte deine Sprachreise noch heute unter https://partners.rosettastone.com/safiyanygaard und sichere dir einen exklusiven Rabatt von über 60 % auf ein unbegrenztes, lebenslanges Sprachabo! 🍡

#rosettastone #rosettastonepartner

HALLO FREUNDE! Und willkommen zum 7-Eleven-Einkauf meiner Träume! Auf unseren vorherigen Reisen nach Ostasien fiel uns die große Präsenz von 7-Eleven-Läden auf – und wir waren nicht nur überrascht, wie weit verbreitet und beliebt sie waren, sondern merkten auch schnell, dass sie viele tolle Sachen hatten, die es in den USA nicht gibt – wie Baos, Tees, Sandos, Nudeln, Eiskaffee, einzigartige Chipssorten, Pfannkuchen-Sandwiches, Maiseis – und vieles mehr! Und als wir zurückkamen, fiel mir auf, wie viele Leute online auch internationale 7-Eleven-Läden besuchten und Snacks kauften – und mir wurde klar: Das ist eine Convenience-Store-Bewegung!

Auf unseren Reisen im letzten Jahr haben wir 7-Eleven-Touren und -Besuche in jedem unserer Länder – Singapur, Malaysia und Japan – gesammelt, um ein paar virale Snacks zu probieren und sie generell zu vergleichen, aber vor allem auch einfach nur, um zu schlemmen! Welchen 7-Eleven in welchem ​​Land sollten wir als Nächstes besuchen?

Außerdem gibt es eine Kontroverse um Vogelnestprodukte, von der wir vor den Dreharbeiten nichts wussten. Wir bitten um Entschuldigung. Wenn Sie mehr erfahren möchten, finden Sie hier ein paar Links zu weiteren Informationen:

pl.description:
Jeszcze raz dziękujemy Rosetta Stone za sponsorowanie tego filmu!! Rozpocznij swoją językową podróż już dziś na stronie https://partners.rosettastone.com/safiyanygaard, aby uzyskać ekskluzywną zniżkę ponad 60% na nieograniczoną dożywotnią subskrypcję językową!! 🍡

#rosettastone #rosettastonepartner

CZEŚĆ PRZYJACIELE!! I witajcie w 7-Eleven haul moich marzeń!! Teraz, podczas naszych poprzednich podróży do Azji Wschodniej, zdecydowanie zauważyliśmy powszechność 7-Eleven prawie wszędzie - i nie tylko byliśmy zaskoczeni, jak powszechne i popularne były - szybko zdaliśmy sobie sprawę, że mają wiele naprawdę niesamowitych rzeczy, których nie mamy w Stanach - takich jak bao, herbaty, sando, makarony, mrożone kawy, unikalne smaki chipsów, kanapki naleśnikowe, lody kukurydziane - i wiele więcej!! A kiedy wróciliśmy - zacząłem zauważać, jak wiele osób online również chodzi do międzynarodowych 7-Eleven i robi przekąski - i zdałem sobie sprawę - to jest ruch sklepów typu convenience store!!

Więc podczas naszych podróży w ciągu ostatniego roku zebraliśmy wycieczki i zakupy 7-Eleven w każdym kraju, który odwiedziliśmy - Singapurze, Malezji i Japonii... aby wypróbować kilka popularnych przekąsek i ogólnie je porównać, ale także głównie po to, aby ucztować! W którym kraju 7-Eleven powinniśmy odwiedzić następnym razem? 

Ponadto, istnieje pewna kontrowersja wokół produktów z ptasich gniazd, o której nie wiedzieliśmy przed filmowaniem, przepraszamy. Jeśli chcesz dowiedzieć się więcej, oto kilka linków do dodatkowych informacji -

pt-BR.title: Eu comi em 7-Elevens pela Ásia
pt-BR.description:
Mais uma vez, obrigado à Rosetta Stone por patrocinar este vídeo!! Comece sua jornada linguística hoje mesmo em https://partners.rosettastone.com/safiyanygaard e ganhe um desconto exclusivo de mais de 60% em uma assinatura vitalícia ilimitada de idiomas!! 🍡

#rosettastone #rosettastonepartner

OLÁ, AMIGOS!! E bem-vindos à compra de 7-Elevens dos meus sonhos!! Em nossas viagens anteriores ao Leste Asiático, notamos a predominância de 7-Elevens em praticamente todos os lugares - e não só ficamos surpresos com o quão difundidos e populares eles eram, como rapidamente percebemos que eles tinham muitas coisas incríveis que não temos nos Estados Unidos - como baos, chás, sandos, macarrão instantâneo, cafés gelados, sabores únicos de salgadinhos, sanduíches de panqueca, sorvete de milho - e muito mais!! E quando voltamos, comecei a notar quantas pessoas online também estavam indo a 7-Elevens internacionais e comprando lanches - e percebi - isso é um movimento de loja de conveniência!!

Então, em nossas viagens ao longo do ano passado, coletamos informações sobre passeios e compras na 7-Eleven em cada país que visitamos — Cingapura, Malásia e Japão... para experimentar alguns petiscos virais e compará-los em geral, mas também principalmente para nos deliciarmos! Qual 7-Eleven de qual país devemos visitar em seguida?

Além disso, há uma controvérsia em torno de produtos feitos com ninhos de pássaros da qual não tínhamos conhecimento antes das filmagens. Pedimos desculpas. Se quiser saber mais, aqui estão alguns links para mais informações -

皆さん、こんにちは！ 夢のセブンイレブン巡りへようこそ！ これまでの東アジア旅行で、セブンイレブンがいたるところに溢れていることを実感しました。その広さと人気ぶりに驚いただけでなく、アメリカにはない素晴らしい商品がたくさんあることにもすぐに気づきました。例えば、包子、お茶、サンドイッチ、麺類、アイスコーヒー、ユニークなチップスフレーバー、パンケーキサンドイッチ、コーンアイスクリームなどなど！ そして帰国後、オンラインで多くの人が海外のセブンイレブンを訪れ、スナック巡りをしていることに気づき始めました。そして、これはコンビニエンスストアのムーブメントだと気づきました！

ということで、この1年間の旅で訪れた各国（シンガポール、マレーシア、日本）のセブンイレブン巡りとお土産集めをしてきました。話題のスナックを試したり、比較したり、もちろんただお腹いっぱい食べたりするのが目的でした！次はどの国のセブンイレブンに行こうかな？

それから、撮影前には知らなかったのですが、ツバメの巣に関する論争がありました。申し訳ありません。さらに詳しく知りたい方は、以下のリンクから詳細情報をご覧ください。

fr-FR.title: J'ai mangé dans des 7-Elevens à travers l'Asie
fr-FR.description:
Merci encore à Rosetta Stone pour le sponsoring de cette vidéo ! Commencez votre voyage linguistique dès aujourd'hui sur https://partners.rosettastone.com/safiyanygaard et bénéficiez d'une réduction exclusive de plus de 60 % sur un abonnement linguistique illimité à vie ! 🍡

#rosettastone #rosettastonepartner

BONJOUR LES AMIS ! Et bienvenue dans le 7-Eleven de mes rêves ! Lors de nos précédents voyages en Asie de l'Est, nous avions constaté la présence des 7-Eleven un peu partout. Non seulement nous avons été surpris par leur popularité, mais nous avons vite réalisé qu'ils proposaient plein de produits vraiment géniaux que nous n'avons pas aux États-Unis : baos, thés, sandos, nouilles, cafés glacés, chips aux saveurs uniques, pancakes, glaces au maïs, et bien plus encore ! À notre retour, j'ai remarqué que de nombreux internautes fréquentaient également les 7-Eleven internationaux pour faire leurs courses de snacks. J'ai alors réalisé qu'il s'agissait d'un mouvement de proximité !

Au cours de nos voyages de l'année dernière, nous avons rassemblé des circuits et des hauls 7-Eleven dans chaque pays que nous avons visité : Singapour, la Malaisie et le Japon… pour tester des en-cas devenus virals et les comparer, mais aussi et surtout pour nous régaler ! Quel pays 7-Eleven devrions-nous visiter ensuite ?

De plus, il existe une controverse autour des produits à base de nids d'oiseaux dont nous n'avions pas connaissance avant le tournage, veuillez nous en excuser. Pour en savoir plus, voici quelques liens :

HALO TEMAN-TEMAN!! Dan selamat datang di 7-Eleven impian saya!! Nah, pada perjalanan kami sebelumnya ke Asia Timur, kami benar-benar memperhatikan banyaknya 7-Eleven di mana-mana - dan kami tidak hanya terkejut dengan seberapa luas dan populernya mereka - kami segera menyadari, mereka memiliki banyak barang yang sangat mengagumkan yang tidak kami miliki di Amerika Serikat - seperti, bao, teh, sando, mi, es kopi, rasa keripik yang unik, sandwich panekuk, es krim jagung - dan banyak lagi!! Jadi dalam perjalanan kami selama setahun terakhir, kami telah mengumpulkan tur dan belanja 7-Eleven di setiap negara yang kami kunjungi - Singapura, Malaysia, dan Jepang… untuk mencoba beberapa camilan viral, dan membandingkannya secara umum, tetapi juga sebagian besar hanya untuk berpesta! 7-Eleven negara mana yang harus kami kunjungi selanjutnya?

안녕하세요, 친구들!! 꿈꿔왔던 세븐일레븐 쇼핑에 오신 것을 환영합니다!! 지난 동아시아 여행에서 세븐일레븐이 거의 모든 곳에 있다는 것을 확실히 알게 되었어요. 세븐일레븐의 광활한 분포와 인기에 놀랐을 뿐만 아니라, 미국에는 없는 멋진 상품들이 많다는 것을 금방 알아차렸죠. 바오, 차, 샌도, 국수, 아이스 커피, 독특한 감자튀김 맛, 팬케이크 샌드위치, 콘 아이스크림 등등! 그리고 돌아오자마자 온라인에서 해외 세븐일레븐에 가서 간식을 구매하는 사람들이 얼마나 많은지 알게 되었어요. 그리고 이게 바로 편의점 운동이라는 걸 깨달았죠!!

그래서 지난 한 해 동안 싱가포르, 말레이시아, 일본 등 각 나라를 여행하며 세븐일레븐 투어와 하울(haul)을 모아서 인기 간식들을 먹어보고 비교해 보기도 했지만, 대부분은 그냥 즐기기 위해서였죠! 다음에는 어느 나라의 세븐일레븐을 방문해야 할까요?

그리고, 새둥지 관련 제품에 대한 논란이 있는데, 촬영 전에는 미처 몰랐던 부분입니다. 양해 부탁드립니다. 더 자세히 알고 싶으시다면, 다음 링크를 통해 더 많은 정보를 얻으실 수 있습니다.

HALLO VRIENDEN!! En welkom bij de 7-Eleven-aankoop van mijn dromen!! Tijdens onze eerdere reizen naar Oost-Azië merkten we zeker hoe wijdverspreid en populair 7-Elevens waren - en we waren niet alleen verrast door hoe wijdverspreid en populair ze waren - we realiseerden ons al snel dat ze veel geweldige dingen hadden die we in de Verenigde Staten niet hebben - zoals bao's, thee, sando's, noedels, ijskoffie, unieke smaken chips, pannenkoekensandwiches, maïsijs ​​- en meer!! En toen we terugkwamen, begon ik te merken hoeveel mensen online ook naar internationale 7-Elevens gingen en snacks kochten - en ik besefte - dit is een gemakswinkelbeweging!!

Tijdens onze reizen van het afgelopen jaar hebben we 7-Eleven-tours en -hauls verzameld in elk land dat we bezochten - Singapore, Maleisië en Japan... om wat virale snacks uit te proberen en ze te vergelijken, maar vooral ook gewoon om te smullen! Welk 7-Eleven-land moeten we als volgende bezoeken?

Er is ook wat controverse rond vogelnestproducten waar we vóór de opnames niet van op de hoogte waren. Onze excuses daarvoor. Wil je meer weten? Hier zijn een paar links naar meer informatie:

it.title: Ho mangiato nei 7-Eleven in tutta l'Asia
it.description:
Grazie ancora a Rosetta Stone per aver sponsorizzato questo video!! Inizia il tuo viaggio linguistico oggi stesso su https://partners.rosettastone.com/safiyanygaard per uno sconto esclusivo di oltre il 60% su un abbonamento linguistico illimitato a vita!! 🍡

#rosettastone #rosettastonepartner

CIAO AMICI!! E benvenuti al viaggio da 7-Eleven dei miei sogni!! Ora, nei nostri precedenti viaggi in Asia orientale, abbiamo sicuramente notato la presenza di 7-Eleven praticamente ovunque - e non solo siamo rimasti sorpresi dalla loro diffusione e popolarità - ma ci siamo subito resi conto che avevano un sacco di cose fantastiche che non abbiamo negli Stati Uniti - come bao, tè, sando, noodles, caffè freddo, patatine dai gusti unici, panini con pancake, gelato al mais - e molto altro!! E una volta tornati, ho iniziato a notare quante persone online andavano anche nei 7-Eleven internazionali e facevano viaggi di snack - e ho capito: questo è un movimento da minimarket!!

Quindi, durante i nostri viaggi dell'ultimo anno, abbiamo raccolto tour e haul di 7-Eleven in ogni paese che abbiamo visitato: Singapore, Malesia e Giappone... per provare alcuni snack virali e, in generale, confrontarli, ma anche e soprattutto per fare un piccolo assaggio! Quale 7-Eleven di quale paese dovremmo visitare la prossima volta?

Inoltre, ci sono alcune controversie sui prodotti a base di nidi d'uccello di cui non eravamo a conoscenza prima delle riprese, ci scusiamo. Se desideri saperne di più, ecco un paio di link per ulteriori informazioni:

snippet.title: Mid-East Crisis escalates - Iran rains missiles on Israel after attacks on nuclear sites | BBC News
snippet.description:
Iran has launched mass new strikes on Israel.  It says it attacked dozens of targets including military centres and airbases.   Smoke has been seen rising over the skyscrapers of Tel Aviv and there have been explosions in Jerusalem.  

The  bombardment is in retaliation for Israel's strikes on Iran, hitting military and nuclear sites.   It says it hit a nuclear facility in Isfahan following earlier strikes on the country's biggest nuclear facility at Natanz .Israel said the attacks were vital to prevent Iran developing a nuclear weapon.  

Iran’s spiritual leader, Ayatollah Khamenei, promised his country would 'inflict heavy blows' in response.
 
There are warnings the conflict could escalate into all-out war.  

Jane Hill presents BBC News at Ten reporting by Lucy Williamson, Ione Wells, Frank Gardner, Tom Bateman, Gary O’Donoghue and Lyse Doucet. 

Subscribe here: http://bit.ly/1rbfUog

snippet.title: First Class on the World's Newest Airline (Global Airlines)
snippet.description:
Get $50 off Daily Drop Pro! - https://s.dailydrop.com/yt_kn-summer25
Our FREE Miles & Points 101 Course - https://s.dailydrop.com/kn_101
Our FREE Daily Drop Newsletter - https://s.dailydrop.com/kn_sign-up

Join us on our first inaugural flight experience!! We flew on Global Airlines first ever flight from Manchester Airport to JFK, New York in first class! This airline was started buy a guy who we've followed on instagram for years and had never met...until today ;)

Huge thanks to James and the Global Airlines team for having us on this unforgettable flight! (and for giving us 50% off our tickets!)

Episode 962 | Filmed May 2025

Subscribe to our new friend  @jameswarrenolivertravelexpert  :)
 https://youtu.be/W92wnw7Ytq8?si=yj_Jm5asGT03YMJo 

——————————————————

Who are Kara and Nate?! 

2016-2019: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=FuFv4iF8wgg&t=1s 

2020-2024: https://youtu.be/ikAN9e0gBaU?si=G644UGWIqPrOzTYW

Originally from Nashville, Tennessee, we got married 2013 and were super “normal.” I was a teacher and Nate started a small printing business from the spare bedroom of our apartment. 

We discovered the world of “travel hacking” while planning our honeymoon & became addicted ;)

So after 2 years of obsessively saving $35k and over 2 million miles and points, we sold our cars and apartment and left home January 10, 2016 for a “one year” trip around the world.

Our goal was to see as many places as possible before we ran out of money and went back home to “normal life.” We started this channel to share our experiences with friends and family, but quickly fell in love with living on the road and found a new passion for capturing our travels through video. So we did everything we could to keep going.

4 years later, we achieved our new goal of visiting 100 countries and all 7 continents. We had no plans to slow down, until 2020 forced us to ;) Which is when we bought a converted van to start exploring our own country for the first time!

After ~2 years of van life, we are back to full time international traveling! And now we are in our 10TH YEAR of finding the best adventures the world has to offer :) 

We are incredibly grateful to be able to continue doing something we love every day. 😊🎥🌎 Thank you to everyone who has been a part of our journey!

21:30 visiting upstairs business class
22:56 addressing the negative reviews

24:54 final thoughts

snippet.title: Epic Fire Experiments w/ Unspeakable!
snippet.description:
Welcome to the second week of Camp CrunchLabs! This week Unspeakable joins us for some epic fire experiments! It's not too late to join Camp CrunchLabs! Join here: http://www.campcrunchlabs.com 

Check out Disney's Elio, only in theaters June 20: https://movies.disney.com/elio
#Elio

Each build-it-yourself STEM toy teaches the magic and fun in engineering principles and coincides with exclusive weekly videos like this one that accelerate your learning! Ready for Camp? Visit http://www.campcrunchlabs.com for more info.

A big thanks to our special guest @Unspeakable  for joining me on Venus!

Week 1 Super Challenge Montage: https://youtu.be/O-zch46IFSY?si=N-ypEfL2RpXTcExw

This weeks Challenge:
HACK YOUR FOOD LIKE AN ENGINEER!
This 10-Day challenge requires you to embrace the wonderful world of food. Solve a food problem - like food that's too crummy or spills too easily or that needs a clever protection. Maybe you can come up with a smart way to make a CrunchLab logo out of food, or build a device that makes cooking easier, or maybe engineer something to feed yourself.

As always, be safe and get a parent's permission before building. Once you've filmed it, work with your parents to share it with us!"

HOW TO SUBMIT YOUR CHALLENGES?
Parents: Tag challenge project video submissions @crunchlabs with #CampCrunchlabsContest on Instagram, X, TikTok or Facebook. Then complete this form https://www.crunchlabs.com/pages/camp-planet-page-venus

NO PURCHASE NECESSARY. Contest begins at 9:00 a.m. PT on 6/7/25 & ends 11:59 p.m. PT on 7/23/25; but, to be eligible to win Grand Prize, one must enter by 11:59 p.m. PT on 7/8/25. Open to legal residents of the 50 U.S. & D.C., who are 18+ and the parent or legal guardian of at least (1) child between 8-16 years of age. Grand Prize winner must travel 7/20/25-7/22/25. See Official Rules for full details including entry periods, entry requirements, prize descriptions and judging criteria. Void where prohibited.
Full rules: http://crunchlabs.com/camp-rules

snippet.title: Rainbow Candy Series 🍭 RED - Cherry Doll
snippet.description:
Colors + Candy Theme = Perfection?! Come with me and indulge in this sugary sweet series of dolls with the first of six to come: Red!
--------------------------------------------
Merchandise https://www.dollightful.shop/
Doll clothing patterns for sale: https://www.etsy.com/shop/DollightfulPatterns
Instagram, Twitter, Pinterest: @dollightfully
--------------------------------------------
MATERIALS:
Monster High Doll “Draculaura” (Generation 3)
Nylon doll hair from https://dollyhair.com/
Doll hair tools from https://www.etsy.com/shop/TheDollPlanetHair
Rooting tool and needles (drill chuck + needle with its eye cut at an angle)
Mr.Super Clear UV Flat (wear a mask and spray in a ventilated area!)
Mask - Organic Vapor Particle Respirator Mask 
Gouache paint
Water colored Pencils -Faber Castell
High Gloss Varnish – Liquitex
Air Dry Clay -Premier
Acrylic paint – Liquitex, Alpha
Literal trash I found on the ground (Mylar ballon, vinyl packaging)
--------------------------------------------
SPOONFLOWER (fabric printing service) info….
For cotton, I chose their “Petal Signature Cotton” option on the “1 yard (42”x36”)”. My file size was 6300x5400px, 150 dpi.
For stretchy knit, I chose their “Jersey1” option on the “fat quarter (28”x18”)”. My file size was 4200x2700px, 150 dpi.
For satin, I chose their “Satin1” option on the “fat quarter (27”x18”)”. My file size was 4050x2700px, 150 dpi.
--------------------------------------------
Dollightful theme song “Bubble Pop” was made in Garage Band using royalty-free loops.
Other musical tracks & SFX from Artlist https://artlist.io 
Ariel Shalom – Raindrops (Instrumental Version)
Jimit – Looku Looku (Instrumental Version)
Saggie – Easty to Love (Instrumental Version)
Aves – God is a Girl (Instrumental Version)
LOLEK – Cruise Control
Rex Banner – Weekend (Instrumental Version)
Lemon – Plastic Generation (Instrumental Version)
--------------------------------------------
Logo and some graphics designed by: https://charliesparksdesign.myportfolio.com/
Some graphics designed by me.
--------------------------------------------
#red #candy #doll

ja.description:

--------------------------------------------
商品 https://www.dollightful.shop/
ドール服型紙販売中: https://www.etsy.com/shop/DollightfulPatterns
Instagram、Twitter、Pinterest: @dollightfully
--------------------------------------------
材料:
モンスターハイドール「ドラキュローラ」（第3世代）
ナイロンドールヘア（https://dollyhair.com/）
ドールヘア用ツール（https://www.etsy.com/shop/TheDollPlanetHair）
植毛用具と針（ドリルチャックと針の穴を斜めにカットしたもの）
Mr.スーパークリアUVフラット（マスクを着用し、換気の良い場所でスプレーしてください！）

ガッシュ絵の具
水彩色鉛筆：ファーバーカステル
高光沢ワニス：リキテックス
エアドライクレイ：プレミア
アクリル絵の具：リキテックス、アルファ
地面に落ちていたゴミ（マイラーバルーン、ビニール包装）

SPOONFLOWER（布地プリントサービス）情報…
綿素材には、「1ヤード（42インチ×36インチ）」の「Petal Signature Cotton」オプションを選択しました。ファイルサイズは6300×5400ピクセル、150dpiでした。
伸縮性のあるニット素材には、「ファットクォーター（28インチ×18インチ）」の「Jersey1」オプションを選択しました。ファイルサイズは4200×2700ピクセル、150dpiでした。

LYRICS
I check the doors, check the windows, and pull the blinds,
I check the clock, wondering what he’ll pull this time,
I have a feeling that necromancer’s outside,
And I’m just trying to stay quiet.

I don’t sleep much, that's crazy, how’d you know that?
Keep myself up, that's maybe how you know that,
Promises and contracts I used to keep,
I don’t sleep much, that's crazy, how’d you know that?
Keep myself up, that’s maybe how you know that,
My hallucination I used to see.

Wake up and I find out, did a change up,
Wait — Did it change up?
Is it light out yet?
Better find out. Bet,
Imma walk around the edge of the room,
And the bed where I hide my face,
Pace around,
Better try to breathe,
Pace around, Pace around.

(Sleep I found)
I wanna get out there,
But I don’t try,
I wanna get out there,
But I don’t try.

I used to see,
It felt so real,
But now I plead,
Just take the deal,
I promised you,
A contract.

snippet.title: Explosions heard in Tel Aviv as Iran launches retaliatory missiles at Israel
snippet.description:
Iran has launched retaliatory missiles at Israel. Projectiles were seen flying across Tel Aviv’s night sky and at least one evaded Israel’s air defence system to strike the ground.
Subscribe to Guardian News on YouTube ► http://bit.ly/guardianwiressub

The Israeli military said its defence systems were operating to intercept ‘the threat’ and that the public had been instructed to ‘enter a protected space and remain there until further notice’. Iran’s Revolutionary Guards said that they carried out attacks against dozens of targets in the country. The response from Iran comes after Israeli strikes hit more than 100 targets in Iran, including nuclear facilities 

Middle East crisis – live updates ► https://www.theguardian.com/world/live/2025/jun/13/israel-iran-strikes-defence-minister-tehran-middle-east-live

snippet.title: YOU Ranked My Characters. I'm SHOCKED.
snippet.description:
___UPLOAD SCHEDULE___

Friday at 4:00pm ET

___________WELCOME TO MY CHANNEL__________

Hey! my name is Moriah (pronounced muh-rye-yuh) Elizabeth and this is my channel....obviously. I'm 30 and like doing creative activities (mostly painting on things), or really anything that gives me an excuse to use rainbows, sprinkles and my own cutesy characters in excess. I'm heavy into editing, so my video are chok-full of sound effects, filters and lil....moments, or as we like to call them "MEmes." I paint on squishies, thrift store finds, and various other items I find. I also love to draw, traditionally and digitally. I'm not the most skilled artist out here, but I like to focus on having fun with creativity and being able to laugh at my own mistakes. 

CURRENT SERIES:
Squishy Makeovers: Fixing and decorating used squishies sent from my viewers
Thrift Store Makeovers: Fixing and decorating stuff I find at thrift stores/yard sales
Bake With ME: Recreating squishies I've decorated in real life
Create This Book: Drawing in the prompt book that I wrote (available to purchase and follow along)
Squishy Unboxing: Opening used squishy packages sent from viewers
Drawings to Squishies: turning my flat drawings into squishies
Finishing Art Ideas: Choosing art ideas from my giant list and making them happen
Squishies I've Been Avoiding: Painting on the squishies I DON'T want to paint

snippet.title: Reflection Point at Rockefeller Center: Google Labs x Wade and Leta
snippet.description:
See how artists Wade and Leta teamed up with Google Labs' generative imagery experiment, Whisk, to help inspire the creation of Reflection Point: their vibrant mirrored maze coming to Rockefeller Center from June 5 to July 20, 2025. This video explores the year-long collaboration, their thoughts on creative style, and how Whisk can help artists reimagine their creative processes.

Try Whisk: https://labs.google/fx/tools/whisk

snippet.title: The Summer I Turned Pretty Season 3 - Official Trailer | Prime Video
snippet.description:
Life’s too short not to spend it with the person you love. The final season of The Summer I Turned Pretty begins July 16.

It’s the end of her junior year of college, and Belly’s looking forward to another summer in Cousins with her soulmate, Jeremiah. Her future seems set, until some core-shaking events bring her first love Conrad back into her life. Now on the brink of adulthood, Belly finds herself at a crossroads and must decide which brother has her heart. Summer will never be the same…

snippet.title: The Sims 4 Enchanted by Nature | Official Reveal Trailer
snippet.description:
The Sims™ 4 Enchanted by Nature Expansion Pack* arrives July 10 and is available for pre-order now: http://ea.com/games/the-sims/the-sims-4/buy/addon/the-sims-4-enchanted-by-nature-expansion-pack


Order now through Aug 21 for the Fairy Garden Digital Content**: the Lofty Leaf Pond, Luminous Mycena Lantern, and Disguised Dwelling Fairy Home.

Indulge your sense of wonder: https://www.ea.com/games/the-sims/the-sims-4/news/enchanted-by-nature-expansion-pack
Live surrounded by nature and embrace a free spirited lifestyle. Who needs beds and plumbing? It's time to get comfy in the great outdoors by meeting your Sims' needs in nature and Foraging for food and collectables. 

There's a charming world to explore, and it has a mystical side. Experience strange Ailments, craft Elixirs, and even become a Fairy! When creating Fairy Sims, you'll choose from a variety of beautiful wings which you can paint freely.

Available July 10 at 10AM PT on EA App PC/Mac, Steam, Xbox One, Xbox Series X|S, PlayStation®4, and PlayStation®5. Pre-order now: http://ea.com/games/the-sims/the-sims-4/buy/addon/the-sims-4-enchanted-by-nature-expansion-pack 

*Requires The Sims 4 & all game updates. For PC, see minimum system requirements for the pack.

**CONDITIONS AND RESTRICTIONS APPLY. http://ea.com/games/the-sims/the-sims-4/buy/addon/the-sims-4-enchanted-by-nature-expansion-pack

snippet.title: Superman | Tickets on Sale Now
snippet.description:
On July 11, the entire world will look up. Get tickets now for #Superman - Only In Theaters and @IMAX 

“Superman,” DC Studios’ first feature film to hit the big screen, is set to soar into theaters worldwide this summer from Warner Bros. Pictures.  In his signature style, James Gunn takes on the original superhero in the newly imagined DC universe with a singular blend of epic action, humor and heart, delivering a Superman who’s driven by compassion and an inherent belief in the goodness of humankind. 

DC Studios heads Peter Safran and Gunn are producing the film, which Gunn directs from his own screenplay, based on characters from DC, Superman created by Jerry Siegel and Joe Shuster.

The film stars David Corenswet (“Twisters,” “Hollywood”) in the dual role of Superman/Clark Kent, Rachel Brosnahan (“The Marvelous Mrs. Maisel”) as Lois Lane and Nicholas Hoult (the “X-Men” movies, “Juror #2”) as Lex Luthor.  The film also stars Edi Gathegi (“For All Mankind”), Anthony Carrigan (“Barry,” “Gotham”), Nathan Fillion (the “Guardians of the Galaxy” films, “The Suicide Squad”), Isabela Merced (“Alien Romulus”), Skyler Gisondo (“Licorice Pizza,” “Booksmart”), Sara Sampaio (“At Midnight”), María Gabriela de Faría (“The Moodys”), Wendell Pierce (“Selma,” “Tom Clancy’s Jack Ryan”), Alan Tudyk (“Andor”), Pruitt Taylor Vince (“Bird Box”) and Neva Howell (“Greedy People”).

“Superman” is executive produced by Nikolas Korda, Chantal Nong Vo and Lars Winther.  Behind the camera, Gunn is joined by frequent collaborators, including director of photography Henry Braham, production designer Beth Mickle, costume designer Judianna Makovsky and composer John Murphy, along with composer David Fleming (“The Last of Us”) and editors William Hoy (“The Batman”) and Craig Alpert (“Deadpool 2,” “Blue Beetle”).  

DC Studios Presents a Troll Court Entertainment/The Safran Company Production, A James Gunn Film, “Superman,” which will be in theaters and IMAX® nationwide on July 11, 2025, and internationally beginning 9 July 2025, distributed by Warner Bros. Pictures.

snippet.title: Kehlani - Folded [Official Visualizer]
snippet.description:
Kehlani - Folded
"Folded' out now! 👔🧺
Stream/DL: https://Kehlani.lnk.to/FoldedID

Subscribe for more official content from Kehlani:
https://Atlantic.lnk.to/KehlaniSubscribe

Follow Kehlani
https://www.kehlani.com/
https://facebook.com/Kehlanimusic
https://twitter.com/Kehlani
https://instagram.com/kehlani

Subscribe for the latest official music videos, official audio videos, performances, behind the scenes and more from Kehlani: https://Atlantic.lnk.to/KehlaniSubscribe

The official YouTube channel of Atlantic Records artist Kehlani.

It doesn’t really need an explanation—you know exactly what Kehlani means when she sings. Without sugarcoating or softening a word, the Bay Area-born two-time GRAMMY® Award-nominated multiplatinum songstress will drop a hard truth in one breath and flip a middle finger in the next. She may extend a seductive invitation or an empathetic plea before leaving you in your thoughts and feelings. Either way, she finds a way to consistently relate without filter. With each move, she strengthens this connection to listeners everywhere.  Kehlani’s 2015 breakout mixtape You Should Be Here received a 2016 GRAMMY® Award nod in the category of “Best Urban Contemporary Album.” On its heels, her 2017 full-length debut SweetSexySavage bowed at #3 on the Billboard Top 200 and eventually went gold. Between selling out dates on the SweetSexySavage Tour, the record closed out the year on Pitchfork’s “The 50 Best Albums of 2017” and Rolling Stone’s “20 Best R&B Albums of 2017.” 

Along the way, she contributed to Suicide Squad: The Album and The Fate of the Furious: The Album and guested on Cardi B’s double-platinum “Ring,” Kyle’s platinum “PLAYINWITME,” and Justin Bieber’s “Get Me,” to name a few. By 2020, she picked up three gold solo singles—"You Should Be Here,” “Honey,” and “Distraction,” for which she received her second GRAMMY® nomination for Best R&B performance. In addition, four platinum singles—“Gangsta,” “The Way” [feat. Chance the Rapper], “CRZY,” and “Nights Like This” [feat. Ty Dolla $ign] and streams in the billions. Not to mention, Billboard Women In Music honored her with the “Rule Breaker Award” as she gathered nominations at the Soul Train Awards and the American Music Awards. Plus, she made show-stopping appearances at Voodoo Music + More, Coachella, and beyond. In the aftermath of 2019’s chart-topping While We Wait mixtape, everything changed. She became a mom. As such, parenthood left an indelible imprint on her second full-length, It Was Good Until It Wasn’t. Out May 8th, It Was Good Until It Wasn’t is described by Kehlani as her most mature body of work, featuring songs based on her own real experiences including recently released “Toxic” and “Everybody Business.” In the end, you’ll know exactly what’s on Kehlani’s mind, heart, and soul on It Was Good Until It Wasn’t.

#Kehlani #Folded #OfficialAudio

What is Roblox? ROBLOX is an online virtual playground and workshop, where kids of all ages can safely interact, create, have fun, and learn. It’s unique in that practically everything on ROBLOX is designed and constructed by members of the community. ROBLOX is designed for 13 to 18 year olds, but it is open to people of all ages. Each player starts by choosing an avatar and giving it an identity. They can then explore ROBLOX — interacting with others by chatting, playing games, or collaborating on creative projects. Each player is also given their own piece of undeveloped real estate along with a virtual toolbox with which to design and build anything — be it a navigable skyscraper, a working helicopter, a giant pinball machine, a multiplayer “Capture the Flag” game or some other, yet-to-be-dreamed-up creation. There is no cost for this first plot of virtual land. By participating and by building cool stuff, ROBLOX members can earn specialty badges as well as ROBLOX dollars (“Robux”). In turn, they can shop the online catalog to purchase avatar clothing and accessories as well as premium building materials, interactive components, and working mechanisms.

#Roblox #foltyn

snippet.title: Pro Chefs Blind Taste Test Every Hot Dog | The Taste Panel | Epicurious

Which hot dogs pack the most bang for your budget, and which should you avoid at all costs?

snippet.title: I Tried the Top 50 Airbnbs in America - Day 2
snippet.description:
hello new mexico!!!
donate here - https://www.stjude.org/50states



Wheel of Doom penalties:
1. Running on fumes - You must drive until the tank says “empty.”
2. Local Legend - You must share a meal with a local from the nearest town before moving on.
3. Route Roulette - You must receive directions from a stranger and follow them word for word.
4. Reverse Card - You must turn around the way you came and find another way to your next Airbnb.
5. Detour - You are not allowed to drive on highways to the next Airbnb.
6. Silent Treatment – No talking between Ryan & Haley for the entire road trip.
7. Airplane Mode - You must get to your next Airbnb without your phones.
8. Locked Out - You are not allowed to sleep in your next Airbnb.
9. The Split - One of you must split up and find another way to your next Airbnb.
10. Red Light, Green Light - Roll a dice — whatever it lands on, you must wait that many hours before hitting the road.
11. Golden Ticket - Congratulations! You have unlocked immunity for 24 hours. It can be activated at any time.

As the early rounds wrapped up, afternoon tee times got underway in Round 1 of the 2025 U.S. Open at Oakmont. J.J. Spaun remains atop the leaderboard, but Sam Burns, Sungjae Im, and Brooks Koepka are close behind. Watch the full midday highlights now!

For live streaming of the U.S. Open and the U.S. Women's Open Presented by Ally, plus live scoring, articles, photos and more, visit usopen.com, uswomensopen.com, and the USGA App.

snippet.title: I Built a Giant LEGO Railway for my Pets!
snippet.description:
#ad To celebrate World Play Day 2025, I partnered with The  @LEGO Group to create the ultimate LEGO railway adventure #LEGOWorldPlayDay #LEGOPartner

I Built a Giant LEGO Railway for my Pets! My LEGO train travels through HUGE mountains, glow-in-the-dark and LED lit tunnels and down an insane DIY pool-noodle spiral coaster. But will the train make it or will this end in a complete disaster? 

♡ Get the merch: https://aquariuminfo.com/ (worldwide shipping 🌎)

SUBSCRIBE for a chance at the ecosystem kit
►  https://www.youtube.com/c/AquariumInfo?sub_confirmation=1

Meet The Crew!
🐈 Nori
🐲 Gizmo
🦀 Noodle & Pickle
🦞 Mochi
🐢 Harry 
🦐 Ralph
🐸 Frito & Burrito
🦎 Lucy & Lemon
🐠 Peanut & Jelly
🦎 Lime & Pepper & Squeak
🪦 R.I.P. Kirby

Watch as we build an insane 200ft LEGO railway through the studio, passing by some of your favorite animals, including Ralph my Peacock Mantis Shrimp, Mochi, my grocery store lobster, and the beloved duo Lucy and Lemon, my axolotls. We even build my kitten Nori a rube goldberg contraption to feed him treats when the train passes by! In this adventure-filled episode, we also travel to an abandoned railway to learn about trains in the real world! 

This LEGO train trip will have 5 epic stops, including a dual greenhouse filled with live plants and LEGO botanicals, a snowy mountain featuring miniature Christmas trees and LEGO Santa, a cat cafe, a glow-in-the-dark tunnel with glowing crystals and an arid desert ecosystem with LEGO animals and real cacti. The LEGO train will be equipped with a tiny camera so you can see what the train sees, so be on the lookout for all of the hidden LEGO builds along the way! Can you spot them all?

Watch until the end to see if the train makes it through the entire trip in one piece! This video is perfect for anyone who loves LEGO trains, building custom LEGO builds, axolotls, exotic pets, rare animals, DIY projects or is just interested in what it takes to build an epic DIY LEGO railway! 

If you have any comments, suggestions or questions for this LEGO train video or future videos, leave them down in the comments! Also for additional content like this, video tutorials, project sneak peeks and more, follow me on Instagram @aquariuminfo.

If you're reading this, you're a Super Fan!
Comment "Cat Cafe" so I notice you 🐈☕️

fr-FR.title: J'ai construit un chemin de fer LEGO géant pour mes animaux de compagnie !
fr-FR.description:
#pub Pour célébrer la Journée mondiale du jeu 2025, je me suis associé au groupe @LEGO pour créer l'aventure ferroviaire LEGO ultime #LEGOWorldPlayDay #LEGOPartner

J'ai construit un train LEGO géant pour mes animaux de compagnie ! Mon train LEGO traverse d'immenses montagnes, des tunnels phosphorescents et éclairés par des LED, et descend un incroyable manège en spirale fait maison. Mais le train survivra-t-il ou cela tournera-t-il au désastre ?

♡ Achetez les produits : https://aquariuminfo.com/ (livraison internationale 🌎)

ABONNEZ-VOUS pour tenter de gagner le kit écosystème
► https://www.youtube.com/c/AquariumInfo?sub_confirmation=1

Découvrez l'équipe ! 🐈 Nori
🐲 Gizmo
🦀 Nouilles et cornichons
🦞 Mochi
🐢 Harry
🦐 Ralph
🐸 Frito et burrito
🦎 Lucy et citron
🐠 Cacahuète et gelée
🦎 Citron vert, poivre et couinement
🪦 R.I.P. Kirby

Regardez-nous construire un incroyable chemin de fer LEGO de 60 mètres à travers le studio, en passant devant certains de vos animaux préférés, dont Ralph, ma crevette-mante paon, Mochi, mon homard d'épicerie, et le duo adoré Lucy et Lemon, mes axolotls. Nous avons même construit un engin Rube Goldberg pour mon chaton Nori afin qu'il puisse lui donner des friandises au passage du train ! Dans cet épisode riche en aventures, nous nous rendons également sur une voie ferrée abandonnée pour en apprendre davantage sur les trains dans le monde réel !

Ce voyage en train LEGO comprendra 5 arrêts exceptionnels, dont une double serre remplie de plantes vivantes et de plantes LEGO, une montagne enneigée avec des sapins de Noël miniatures et le Père Noël LEGO, un café à chats, un tunnel phosphorescent orné de cristaux lumineux et un écosystème désertique aride avec des animaux LEGO et de vrais cactus. Le train LEGO sera équipé d'une minuscule caméra pour que vous puissiez voir ce qu'il voit. Alors, soyez attentifs aux constructions LEGO cachées tout au long du trajet ! Parviendrez-vous à toutes les repérer ?

Regardez la vidéo jusqu'à la fin pour voir si le train termine le voyage en un seul morceau ! Cette vidéo est parfaite pour tous ceux qui aiment les trains LEGO, la construction de constructions LEGO personnalisées, les axolotls, les animaux exotiques, les animaux rares, les projets DIY ou qui s'intéressent simplement à la construction d'un chemin de fer LEGO épique !

Si vous avez des commentaires, des suggestions ou des questions concernant cette vidéo sur le train LEGO ou les prochaines vidéos, n'hésitez pas à les laisser dans les commentaires ! Pour plus de contenu comme celui-ci, des tutoriels vidéo, des aperçus de projets et plus encore, suivez-moi sur Instagram @aquariuminfo.

Si vous lisez ceci, vous êtes un super fan !
Commentez « Cat Cafe » pour que je vous remarque 🐈☕️

ja.title: ペットのために巨大なレゴ鉄道を作りました！
ja.description:
#ad 2025年のワールドプレイデーを記念して、@LEGOグループと提携して究極のレゴ鉄道アドベンチャーを制作しました #LEGOWorldPlayDay #LEGOPartner

ペットのために巨大レゴ鉄道を作りました！レゴの列車は、巨大な山々、暗闇で光るLEDライトのトンネル、そしてDIYで作ったプールヌードルのスパイラルコースターを駆け抜けます。果たして列車は無事に到着できるのでしょうか？それとも大惨事に終わるのでしょうか？

♡ グッズはこちら：https://aquariuminfo.com/ (世界中に発送🌎)

エコシステムキットをゲットするチャンス！チャンネル登録はこちら
► https://www.youtube.com/c/AquariumInfo?sub_confirmation=1

クルーの紹介！
🐈 ノリ
🐲 ギズモ
🦀 ヌードル＆ピクルス
🦞 モチ
🐢 ハリー
🦐 ラルフ
🐸 フリトー＆ブリトー
🦎 ルーシー＆レモン
🐠 ピーナッツ＆ジェリー
🦎 ライム＆ペッパー＆スクイーク
🪦 カービー、安らかに眠れ

スタジオ内を走る全長200フィートのレゴ鉄道を組み立てる様子をご覧ください。お気に入りの動物たちも登場します。私のピーコックシャコのラルフ、スーパーで買ったロブスターのモチ、そして愛しのウーパールーシーとレモン。列車が通る時におやつがもらえる、愛猫のノリのために、ルーブ・ゴールドバーグ風の仕掛けまで作りました！冒険いっぱいのこのエピソードでは、廃線跡にも足を運び、現実世界の列車について学びます！

このレゴ列車の旅には、5つの壮大な停車地点があります。生きた植物とレゴの植物でいっぱいの二重温室、ミニチュアのクリスマスツリーとレゴのサンタが飾られた雪山、猫カフェ、光るクリスタルが輝く暗闇のトンネル、そしてレゴの動物と本物のサボテンが生息する乾燥した砂漠の生態系などです。レゴ列車には小型カメラが搭載されているので、列車が見ているものを見ることができます。道中に隠されたレゴの作品にも注目してください！全部見つけられますか？

列車が無事に全行程を走りきれるか、最後までご覧ください！この動画は、レゴ列車、カスタムレゴ作品の製作、アホロートル、珍しいペット、珍しい動物、DIYプロジェクトが好きな方、あるいは壮大なDIYレゴ鉄道の作り方に興味がある方にぴったりです！

このレゴ列車の動画や今後の動画について、ご意見、ご提案、ご質問がありましたら、コメント欄にお寄せください！このような追加コンテンツ、動画チュートリアル、プロジェクトのプレビューなどについては、Instagram @aquariuminfo をフォローしてください。

これを読んでいるあなたは、私の大ファンです！
「Cat Cafe」とコメントして、私に知らせてください🐈☕️

de-DE.title: Ich habe eine riesige LEGO-Eisenbahn für meine Haustiere gebaut!
de-DE.description:
#Anzeige Um den Weltspieltag 2025 zu feiern, habe ich mich mit der @LEGO Group zusammengetan, um das ultimative LEGO Eisenbahn-Abenteuer zu erschaffen. #LEGOWorldPlayDay #LEGOPartner

Ich habe eine riesige LEGO Eisenbahn für meine Haustiere gebaut! Mein LEGO Zug fährt durch riesige Berge, durch im Dunkeln leuchtende und LED-beleuchtete Tunnel und eine verrückte selbstgebaute Poolnudel-Spiralachterbahn hinunter. Aber wird der Zug es schaffen oder endet das Ganze in einer Katastrophe?

♡ Hol dir das Merchandise: https://aquariuminfo.com/ (weltweiter Versand 🌎)

ABONNIERE und sichere dir das Ökosystem-Set
► https://www.youtube.com/c/AquariumInfo?sub_confirmation=1

Triff die Crew!
🐈 Nori
🐲 Gizmo
🦀 Nudeln & Gurke
🦞 Mochi
🐢 Harry
🦐 Ralph
🐸 Frito & Burrito
🦎 Lucy & Zitrone
🐠 Erdnuss & Gelee
🦎 Limette & Pfeffer & Quietsche
🪦 R.I.P. Kirby

Seht zu, wie wir eine wahnsinnige, 60 Meter lange LEGO-Eisenbahn durchs Studio bauen, vorbei an einigen eurer Lieblingstiere, darunter Ralph, mein Pfauen-Mantis-Garnele, Mochi, mein Supermarkt-Hummer, und das geliebte Duo Lucy und Lemon, meine Axolotl. Wir bauen sogar eine Rube-Goldberg-Maschine für mein Kätzchen Nori, damit er Leckerlis bekommt, wenn der Zug vorbeifährt! In dieser abenteuerlichen Folge reisen wir außerdem zu einer verlassenen Eisenbahnstrecke, um etwas über Züge in der realen Welt zu lernen!

Diese LEGO-Zugfahrt umfasst fünf spektakuläre Stopps, darunter ein Doppelgewächshaus mit lebenden Pflanzen und LEGO Pflanzen, einen verschneiten Berg mit Miniatur-Weihnachtsbäumen und LEGO Weihnachtsmann, ein Katzencafé, einen im Dunkeln leuchtenden Tunnel mit leuchtenden Kristallen und ein trockenes Wüstenökosystem mit LEGO Tieren und echten Kakteen. Der LEGO Zug ist mit einer winzigen Kamera ausgestattet, damit Sie sehen können, was der Zug sieht. Halten Sie also unterwegs Ausschau nach all den versteckten LEGO Bauten! Können Sie sie alle entdecken?

Bleiben Sie bis zum Ende dran, um zu sehen, ob der Zug die gesamte Fahrt unbeschadet übersteht! Dieses Video ist perfekt für alle, die LEGO Züge, individuelle LEGO Bauten, Axolotl, exotische Haustiere, seltene Tiere, DIY-Projekte oder einfach nur die Grundlagen einer epischen DIY-LEGO-Eisenbahn lieben!

Wenn Sie Kommentare, Vorschläge oder Fragen zu diesem oder zukünftigen LEGO-Zug-Videos haben, hinterlassen Sie sie gerne in den Kommentaren! Weitere Inhalte wie diese, Video-Tutorials, Projektvorschauen und mehr finden Sie auf Instagram unter @aquariuminfo.

Wenn du das liest, bist du ein Superfan!

pt-BR.title: Eu construí uma ferrovia gigante de LEGO para meus animais de estimação!
pt-BR.description:
#ad Para celebrar o Dia Mundial do Brincar de 2025, fiz uma parceria com o @LEGO Group para criar a aventura ferroviária LEGO definitiva #LEGOWorldPlayDay #LEGOPartner

Construí uma ferrovia LEGO gigante para meus animais de estimação! Meu trem LEGO viaja por montanhas ENORMES, túneis que brilham no escuro e iluminados por LED e por uma montanha-russa espiral DIY de macarrão de piscina. Mas será que o trem conseguirá sobreviver ou isso terminará em um desastre completo?

♡ Compre os produtos: https://aquariuminfo.com/ (envio para todo o mundo 🌎)

INSCREVA-SE para concorrer ao kit ecossistema
► https://www.youtube.com/c/AquariumInfo?sub_confirmation=1

Conheça a equipe!
🐈 Nori
🐲 Gizmo
🦀 Macarrão e Picles
🦞 Mochi
🐢 Harry
🦐 Ralph
🐸 Frito e Burrito
🦎 Lucy e Limão
🐠 Amendoim e Geleia
🦎 Limão e Pimenta e Guincho
🪦 Descanse em Paz, Kirby

Veja como construímos uma ferrovia de LEGO de 60 metros pelo estúdio, passando por alguns dos seus animais favoritos, incluindo Ralph, meu Camarão Louva-a-Deus Pavão, Mochi, minha lagosta de supermercado, e a dupla querida Lucy e Lemon, meus axolotes. Até construímos para o meu gatinho Nori uma engenhoca de Rube Goldberg para alimentá-lo com guloseimas quando o trem passa! Neste episódio cheio de aventuras, também viajamos para uma ferrovia abandonada para aprender sobre trens no mundo real!

Esta viagem de trem LEGO terá 5 paradas épicas, incluindo uma estufa dupla repleta de plantas vivas e botânicos LEGO, uma montanha nevada com árvores de Natal em miniatura e um Papai Noel LEGO, um café para gatos, um túnel que brilha no escuro com cristais brilhantes e um ecossistema desértico árido com animais LEGO e cactos de verdade. O trem LEGO será equipado com uma pequena câmera para que você possa ver o que o trem vê, então fique atento a todas as construções LEGO escondidas ao longo do caminho! Você consegue encontrar todas?

Assista até o final para ver se o trem consegue completar a viagem inteira inteiro! Este vídeo é perfeito para quem ama trens LEGO, construir construções LEGO personalizadas, axolotes, animais de estimação exóticos, animais raros, projetos "faça você mesmo" ou simplesmente está interessado no que é preciso para construir uma ferrovia LEGO épica!

Se você tiver algum comentário, sugestão ou pergunta para este vídeo do trem LEGO ou para vídeos futuros, deixe-os nos comentários! Para mais conteúdo como este, tutoriais em vídeo, prévias de projetos e muito mais, siga-me no Instagram @aquariuminfo.

Se você está lendo isso, você é um Super Fã!
Comente "Cat Cafe" para eu te notar 🐈☕️

it.title: Ho costruito una ferrovia LEGO gigante per i miei animali!
it.description:
#ad Per celebrare la Giornata Mondiale del Gioco 2025, ho collaborato con The @LEGO Group per creare l'avventura ferroviaria LEGO definitiva #LEGOWorldPlayDay #LEGOPartner

Ho costruito una ferrovia LEGO gigante per i miei animali! Il mio treno LEGO attraversa montagne ENORMI, tunnel fosforescenti e illuminati a LED e scende lungo un folle ottovolante a spirale fai da te con tubi galleggianti. Ma il treno ce la farà o finirà in un disastro totale?

♡ Acquista il merchandising: https://aquariuminfo.com/ (spedizioni in tutto il mondo 🌎)

ISCRIVITI per avere la possibilità di vincere il kit ecosistema
► https://www.youtube.com/c/AquariumInfo?sub_confirmation=1

Incontra la squadra! 🐈 Nori
🐲 Gizmo
🦀 Noodle e Cetrioli
🦞 Mochi
🐢 Harry
🦐 Ralph
🐸 Frito e Burrito
🦎 Lucy e Limone
🐠 Arachidi e Marmellata
🦎 Lime e Pepe e Squeak
🪦 R.I.P. Kirby

Guardateci costruire una folle ferrovia LEGO di 60 metri attraverso lo studio, passando accanto ad alcuni dei vostri animali preferiti, tra cui Ralph, la mia Canocchia Pavone, Mochi, la mia aragosta del supermercato, e l'amatissimo duo Lucy e Limone, i miei axolotl. Costruiamo persino un marchingegno Rube Goldberg per dargli dei dolcetti quando passa il treno! In questo episodio pieno di avventure, visitiamo anche una ferrovia abbandonata per imparare a conoscere i treni nel mondo reale!

Questo viaggio in treno LEGO prevede 5 tappe epiche, tra cui una doppia serra piena di piante vive e piante botaniche LEGO, una montagna innevata con alberi di Natale in miniatura e Babbo Natale LEGO, un bar per gatti, un tunnel luminescente con cristalli luminosi e un ecosistema desertico arido con animali LEGO e veri cactus. Il treno LEGO sarà dotato di una minuscola telecamera per permettervi di vedere ciò che vede il treno, quindi tenete gli occhi aperti per tutte le costruzioni LEGO nascoste lungo il percorso! Riuscite a individuarle tutte?

Guardate fino alla fine per vedere se il treno riesce a percorrere l'intero viaggio intatto! Questo video è perfetto per chiunque ami i treni LEGO, costruire costruzioni LEGO personalizzate, axolotl, animali esotici, animali rari, progetti fai da te o sia semplicemente interessato a ciò che serve per costruire una ferrovia LEGO fai da te epica!

Se avete commenti, suggerimenti o domande per questo video sul treno LEGO o per i video futuri, lasciateli nei commenti! Per contenuti aggiuntivi come questo, tutorial video, anteprime di progetti e altro ancora, seguitemi su Instagram @aquariuminfo.

Se stai leggendo questo, sei un Super Fan!
Commenta "Cat Cafe" così ti noto 🐈☕️

Se ami i LEGO, gli ecosistemi, gli animali domestici, i video di salvataggio e gli acquari, guarda i miei altri video!

Nadia questions Reese about lying to Tracy.  Jason unsuccessfully tries to get answers. Kris expresses a new side to her. Bruce tries to mask how he feels in order to save face.

THE LESBIAN HOMIE 4

Three months have passed, and E and Reese are entangled in a secret situationship neither of them can fully define. As Reese wrestles with ending it before things spiral, Bruce believes he's finally free of the drama that comes with the lesbian homies—until he finds himself caught in a new love triangle that tests his integrity. With his closest friends distracted by their own romantic chaos, Bruce leans on an unexpected ally... only to end up right back where he started.

snippet.title: Wiz Khalifa: Tiny Desk Concert
snippet.description:
This Black Music Month, Tiny Desk honors the anniversaries of landmark albums that have shaped the course of music and culture.

Bobby Carter | June 10, 2025
Wiz Khalifa’s Kush & Orange Juice came out 15 years ago. To honor the anniversary, the Pittsburgh emcee assembled a group of Tiny Desk veterans, Pennsylvania natives and his DJ to reimagine highlights from the classic mixtape, plus tracks from Kush & Orange Juice 2, its similar, yet more mature follow-up.

Something was happening during the entire show and lots of us in the room could feel it. We were waiting for him to engage with us, but he didn’t. I stepped in after a few songs to remind him that it was OK to do so — still, nothing. But then, after “Crime Bud and Women,” Wiz spoke to the audience for the first and only time, wiping away tears: “You made me cry. F*** y’all!” 

I can muster up a few guesses as to why the emotion overflowed. Wiz had a host of family and friends present in this very intimate setting, including his father. And he did tell me how much he loves performing. But honestly, this sonic masterpiece was good enough to hit the tear ducts. 

SET LIST
“Red Eye” 
“Mezmorized” 
“The Kid Frankie” 
“Never Been”
“Up”
“Crime Bud and Women” 

MUSICIANS
Wiz Khalifa: vocals
Kenneth Wright: music director, bass
DJ Bonics: turntables
Uncle Bubz: keys
Russell Gelman-Sheehan: guitar
Kendall Lewis: drums

TINY DESK TEAM
Producer: Bobby Carter
Director/Editor: Joshua Bryant
Audio Technical Director: Josh Newell
Video Editor: Kara Frame
Videographers: Joshua Bryant, Kara Frame, Maia Stern
Audio Engineer: Josephine Nyounai
Production Assistants: Ashley Pointer, Dora Levite
Photographer: Catie Dull
Tiny Desk Series Editor: Lars Gotrich
Executive Producer: Suraya Mohamed
Series Creators: Bob Boilen, Stephen Thompson
VP, Visuals and Music: Keith Jenkins

snippet.title: ARGENTINA vs. COLOMBIA [1-1] | RESUMEN | ELIMINATORIAS SUDAMERICANAS | FECHA 16
snippet.description:
¡Emotiva igualdad en Buenos Aires! 🇦🇷🤝🇨🇴

Por la decimosexta fecha de las Eliminatorias Sudamericanas para la Copa del Mundo de la FIFA 2026, jugado este martes en el estadio Monumental en Buenos Aires, la Albiceleste y Colombia empataron 1-1.

‘Lucho’ Díaz a los 24’ abrió el marcador con un golazo para poner en ventaja a la selección ‘cafetera’, pero cerca del final Thiago Almada a los 80’ le dio el empate a la Albiceleste, que jugó un rato con diez jugadores por la expulsión del volante Enzo Fernández.

#EliminatoriasSudamericanas

snippet.description:
Prime Video India Presents
Panchayat Season 4 Official Trailer
Starring Jitendra Kumar, Neena Gupta, Raghubir Yadav, Faisal Malik, Chandan Roy, Sanvikaa, Durgesh Kumar, Sunita Rajwar, Ashok Pathak, Pankaj Jha

A TVF Creation
Created by: Deepak Kumar Mishra, Chandan Kumar
Directed by: Akshat Vijaywargiya, Deepak Kumar Mishra
Written by: Chandan Kumar
Executive Producers: Deepak Kumar Mishra, Vijay Koshy, Shreyansh Pandey

Official Release Date June 24, 2025 on Prime Video India.

About:
Amidst the much-awaited village panchayat elections, Pradhan’s and Bhushan’s camps battle tooth and nail to maintain the upper hand. The future of everyone, including Abhishek, hangs in the balance.

ABOUT PRIME VIDEO
Prime Video is a one-stop entertainment destination offering customers a vast collection of premium programming in one application available across several devices. On Prime Video, customers can find their favourite Indian and international original series, movies, TV shows, and more, across multiple languages – including Indian-produced Original series like Mirzapur, Farzi, Panchayat, The Family Man, Dhootha, Jubilee, Dahaad, Made in Heaven, Suzhal – The Vortex, Inspector Rishi, Poacher, Indian Police Force, Paatal Lok, Rainbow Rishta, Wedding.con; Original movies like Maja Ma, Ammu, Mast Mein Rehne Ka; popular global Originals like Citadel, The Lord of The Rings: The Rings of Power, Fallout, Reacher, The Boys, The Wheel of Time, Road House, The Idea of You; some of the biggest post-theatrical films; direct-to-service films such as Shershaah, Soorarai Pottru, Sardar Udham, Bawaal, Gehraiyaan, Jai Bhim, Jalsa, Sherni, Narappa, Sarpatta Parambarai, Kuruthi, Joji, Malik, Pippa, HOME, Sharmajee Ki Beti, and many more of such titles. Additionally, Prime Video’s video entertainment marketplace, offers customers programming from partners such as Lionsgate Play, Discovery+ Crunchyroll, BBC Player, Sony Pictures – Stream, MGM+, FanCode, Chaupal, Manorama Max, Eros Now, Hoichoi, Anime Times, to name a few, via Prime Video add-on-subscriptions, as well as the option to rent movies, regardless of whether customers have a Prime membership or not. Customers can also go behind the scenes of their favorite movies and series with exclusive X-Ray access. EMOTIONAL INTERVIEW – Behind the scenes of our flooded desert escape, But Our Capitol Gorge Flash Flood Rescue on June 23rd 2022, But Flash Flood Caught on Camera! Little Wild Horse Slot Canyon, But 10 Devastating Flash Floods Caught On Camera, But TRAPPED IN THE SIMPSON DESERT BY FLOODING not seen in 50yrs! What do we do now?, But Running out of fuel, food & water in the Simpson Desert! Do we make it? 10 days, 1000km in low range, But FLOODED & BOGGED! Do we get out? Once in a decade storm Floods Australia’s DRIEST town!, But FLOODED Kimberley river crossing GONE WRONG – 150m+ wide rapids - our most epic trip EVER FILMED!, But 5 4WDs FLOODED IN CAPE YORK - 1 gets towed home! Frenchmans - the WETTEST we've ever seen it!, But Lake Eyre’s biggest flood in nearly 50 years | 7.30, But CARAVANS ABANDONED & stuck for 1 week in flooded Australian Outback! Do we get out?, But THE WETTEST WE'VE SEEN CAPE YORK... RAGING rivers & bottomless mud - 1st 4WDs down Tele Track 2023 or any other video like 4WD 24/7, The Grand Tour, Matts Off Road Recovery, Donut Media or Mighty Car Mods would make. This is a video where Jock & Jesse sit down for a ‘tell all’ chat about escaping a once-in-a-lifetime desert flood!

hi.title: भावनात्मक साक्षात्कार - बाढ़ग्रस्त रेगिस्तान से बचने के हमारे सफर के पीछे की कहानी
hi.description:
82 दिनों के बाद 4WDs की रिकवरी और भावनात्मक साक्षात्कार - बाढ़ग्रस्त रेगिस्तान से भागने के पीछे की कहानी। अब तक आपने सिम्पसन रेगिस्तान की बाढ़ से हमारे जंगली भागने को देखा होगा - लेकिन बहुत कुछ ऐसा है जो आपने नहीं देखा... 🫣

अगर आपने वाकई एपिसोड मिस कर दिए हैं, तो उन्हें यहाँ देखें:
एपिसोड 1: https://youtu.be/816Z-XpB0_s
एपिसोड 2: https://youtu.be/_32oDuTWIPI

जब हम बर्ड्सविले में फंसे हुए थे, तो हमने बर्ड्सविले पब में क्रू के साथ बैठकर पर्दे के पीछे की बातें कीं और कैमरे से छूटी हुई हर बात बताई। एक बीयर लें और सुनें! 🍻

कठिन परिस्थितियों से जूझ रहे ऑस्ट्रेलियाई किसानों की सहायता करें 👉🏻 https://aussiehelpers.org.au/

शॉन, ग्राहम, जॉक और जेसी - जिन्हें पहले 4WD एक्शन के नाम से जाना जाता था - 20+ सालों से ऑस्ट्रेलिया में बेहतरीन ऑफ-रोड कंटेंट दे रहे हैं। बेहतरीन कार बिल्ड और 4x4 टिप्स से लेकर फ्रेजर आइलैंड, यूटा, द किम्बरली, कोलोराडो, द रूबिकॉन ट्रेल और द सिम्पसन डेजर्ट जैसे प्रतिष्ठित स्थानों की खोज तक, हम हर ऑफ-रोडर के लिए कंटेंट बनाते हैं। हमने डोनट मीडिया के दिग्गजों के साथ ट्रैक पर भी काम किया है! चाहे आप पूरी तरह से मॉडिफाइड टोयोटा लैंडक्रूजर चला रहे हों या अपनी हिलक्स या रेंजर से शुरुआत कर रहे हों, हम आपको 4WD और एडवेंचर से जुड़ी हर चीज़ के लिए तैयार रखते हैं।

📱 पर्दे के पीछे की सामग्री के लिए हमारे सोशल मीडिया को फ़ॉलो करें
इंस्टाग्राम 👉🏻 @4wd247
फेसबुक 👉🏻 @4wd247
टिकटॉक 👉🏻 @4wd247

अगर आप यह पढ़ रहे हैं - तो आप एक लीजेंड हैं! नीचे 🤘🏻 के साथ टिप्पणी करें ताकि हम आपको नोटिस कर सकें!

भावनात्मक साक्षात्कार - हमारे बाढ़ वाले रेगिस्तान से बचने के दृश्यों के पीछे, लेकिन 23 जून 2022 को हमारा कैपिटल गॉर्ज फ्लैश फ्लड रेस्क्यू, लेकिन फ्लैश फ्लड कैमरे पर कैद हो गया! लिटिल वाइल्ड हॉर्स स्लॉट कैन्यन, लेकिन 10 विनाशकारी फ्लैश फ्लड कैमरे पर कैद हो गए, लेकिन 50 साल में नहीं देखी गई बाढ़ से सिम्पसन रेगिस्तान में फंस गए! अब हम क्या करें?, लेकिन सिम्पसन रेगिस्तान में ईंधन, भोजन और पानी खत्म हो रहा है! क्या हम इसे बना पाएंगे? 10 दिन, 1000 किमी कम रेंज में, लेकिन बाढ़ और फंस गए! क्या हम बाहर निकल पाएंगे? दशक में एक बार आने वाले तूफान ने ऑस्ट्रेलिया के सबसे सूखे शहर में बाढ़ ला दी!, लेकिन बाढ़ आ गई किम्बर्ले नदी पार करना गलत हो गया - 150 मीटर से अधिक चौड़ी रैपिड्स - हमारी अब तक की सबसे शानदार यात्रा फिल्माई गई!, लेकिन केप यॉर्क में 5 4WD बाढ़ में डूब गए - 1 को घर ले जाया गया! फ्रांसीसी - हमने इसे अब तक देखा सबसे गीला!, लेकिन लेक आयर में लगभग 50 वर्षों में सबसे बड़ी बाढ़ | 7.30, लेकिन कारवां छोड़ दिए गए और बाढ़ वाले ऑस्ट्रेलियाई आउटबैक में 1 सप्ताह तक फंसे रहे! क्या हम बाहर निकलेंगे?, लेकिन केप यॉर्क में हमने जो सबसे गीला दृश्य देखा है... उफनती नदियाँ और अथाह कीचड़ - टेली ट्रैक 2023 पर पहली 4WD या 4WD 24/7, द ग्रैंड टूर, मैट्स ऑफ़ रोड रिकवरी, डोनट मीडिया या माइटी कार मॉड्स जैसे किसी अन्य वीडियो पर। यह एक ऐसा वीडियो है जिसमें जॉक और जेसी एक बार की रेगिस्तानी बाढ़ से बचने के बारे में ‘सब कुछ बताने’ के लिए बैठते हैं!

id.title: WAWANCARA EMOSIONAL – Di balik layar pelarian kami dari banjir di gurun
id.description:

Little Wild Horse Slot Canyon, Namun 10 Banjir Bandang yang Menghancurkan Tertangkap Kamera, Namun TERPERANGKAP DI GURUN SIMPSON OLEH BANJIR yang tidak terlihat dalam 50 tahun! Apa yang harus kami lakukan sekarang?, Namun Kehabisan bahan bakar, makanan & air di Gurun Simpson! Apakah kita berhasil? 10 hari, 1000 km di daerah rendah, Tapi TERBANJIRI & TERJEBAK! Apakah kita bisa keluar? Badai yang terjadi sekali dalam satu dekade Membanjiri kota TERKERING di Australia!, Tapi penyeberangan sungai Kimberley yang TERBANJIRI BERAKHIR – jeram selebar 150 m+ - perjalanan paling epik yang PERNAH DIFILMKAN!, Tapi 5 kendaraan roda empat TERBANJIRI DI CAPE YORK - 1 berhasil diderek pulang! Orang Prancis - yang TERBASAH yang pernah kami lihat!, Tapi banjir terbesar di Danau Eyre dalam hampir 50 tahun | 7.30, Tapi KARAVAN DITINGGALKAN & terjebak selama 1 minggu di pedalaman Australia yang banjir! Apakah kita akan keluar?, Tapi YANG PALING BASAH YANG PERNAH KITA LIHAT DI CAPE YORK... Sungai yang MENGALAMI & lumpur tanpa dasar - 4WD pertama di Tele Track 2023 atau video lain seperti 4WD 24/7, The Grand Tour, Matts Off Road Recovery, Donut Media atau Mighty Car Mods akan membuatnya. Ini adalah video tempat Jock & Jesse duduk untuk mengobrol 'menceritakan semuanya' tentang melarikan diri dari banjir gurun yang terjadi sekali seumur hidup!

ENTREVISTA EMOCIONANTE – Tras bambalinas de nuestra escapada al desierto inundado. Nuestro rescate en la inundación repentina de Capitol Gorge el 23 de junio de 2022. ¡Inundación repentina captada en cámara! Little Wild Horse Slot Canyon. 10 inundaciones repentinas devastadoras captadas en cámara. ¡Atrapados en el desierto de Simpson por inundaciones nunca vistas en 50 años! ¿Qué hacemos ahora? ¡Nos estamos quedando sin combustible, comida ni agua en el desierto de Simpson! ¿Lo logramos? 10 días, 1000 km a baja velocidad, ¡pero inundados y atascados! ¿Salimos? ¡Una tormenta que solo ocurre una vez por década inunda la ciudad más seca de Australia! Pero el cruce del río Kimberley inundado salió mal: rápidos de más de 150 m de ancho. ¡Nuestro viaje más épico JAMÁS FILMADO! Pero 5 4x4 se inundaron en Cabo York, ¡y uno fue remolcado a casa! Frenchmans: ¡la inundación más húmeda que jamás hayamos visto! Pero la mayor inundación del lago Eyre en casi 50 años | 7:30, ¡Pero caravanas abandonadas y atrapadas durante una semana en el interior inundado de Australia! ¿Salimos? Pero lo más húmedo que hemos visto en Cape York... Ríos embravecidos y lodo inagotable. Primeros 4x4 en Tele Track 2023 o cualquier otro video como 4WD 24/7, The Grand Tour, Matts Off Road Recovery, Donut Media o Mighty Car Mods. Este es un video donde Jock y Jesse se reúnen para una charla reveladora sobre cómo escapar de una inundación del desierto única en la vida.

感動インタビュー – 洪水に見舞われた砂漠からの脱出の舞台裏。2022年6月23日、キャピトル・ゴージの洪水救助活動。しかし、洪水の様子はカメラに捉えられていました！リトル・ワイルド・ホース・スロット・キャニオン。10回の壊滅的な洪水がカメラに捉えられていました。しかし、50年ぶりの洪水でシンプソン砂漠に閉じ込められました！さて、どうしよう？, でも、シンプソン砂漠で燃料、食料、水が尽きてしまった！ なんとかたどり着けるかな？ 10日間、低速で1000km走行、でも、洪水と泥沼！ 脱出できるかな？ 10年に一度の嵐がオーストラリアで最も乾燥した町を洪水に襲う！, でも、キンバリー川の横断が失敗に終わり、幅150m以上の急流が流れ込む、これまでで最も壮大な旅になった！, でも、ケープヨークで4WD5台が浸水、1台は自宅まで牽引される！ フレンチマンズ - これまで見た中で最も雨が多い！, でも、エア湖で約50年ぶりの大洪水 | 7.30、でも、キャラバンが放置され、浸水したオーストラリアのアウトバックで1週間足止めされている！脱出できるかな？でも、ケープヨークは今まで見た中で一番の雨…荒れ狂う川と底なしの泥。Tele Track 2023を4WDで初めて下る。あるいは、4WD 24/7、The Grand Tour、Matts Off Road Recovery、Donut Media、Mighty Car Modsなどの動画を参考に。これは、ジョックとジェシーが一生に一度の砂漠の洪水からの脱出について「すべてを語る」動画です！

Little Wild Horse Slot Canyon : 10 inondations soudaines dévastatrices filmées. Piégés dans le désert de Simpson par des inondations inédites depuis 50 ans ! Que faire maintenant ? À court de carburant, de nourriture et d'eau dans le désert de Simpson ! Allons-nous y arriver ? 10 jours, 1 000 km en gamme basse, mais INONDÉS ET ENROULÉS ! On s'en sort ? Une tempête, une fois par décennie, inonde la ville la plus SÈCHE d'Australie !, mais la traversée de la rivière Kimberley INONDÉE a mal tourné – des rapides de plus de 150 m de large – notre voyage le plus épique JAMAIS FILMÉ !, mais 5 4x4 INONDÉS À CAPE YORK – l'un d'eux est remorqué jusqu'à chez lui ! Frenchmans – le PLUS HUMIDE que nous ayons jamais vu !, mais la plus grande inondation du lac Eyre depuis près de 50 ans | 7h30, mais des CARAVANES ABANDONNÉES et coincées pendant 1 semaine dans l'Outback australien inondé ! On s'en sort ? Mais CAPE YORK, c'est LE PLUS MOUILLÉ QU'ON AIE VU... snippet.title: Oilers Complete Game 4 Comeback to Stun Panthers & Even Series | NHL on TNT
snippet.description:

snippet.title: I Tried To Make Something In America (The Smarter Scrubber Experiment) - Smarter Every Day 308
snippet.description:
Get a Smarter Scrubber Here: http://smarterscrubber.com
Interested in Wholesale, or helping us tell the story? Here's a link:
https://forms.gle/XFrLTa5b8kxSvPnu8

I would like to thank the Patrons of Smarter Every Day. They knew about this project early and helped make it happen.
http://www.patreon.com/smartereveryday

John is a great Dad and a good dude. Check out JJGeorge here:
https://www.jjgeorgestore.com/

Our goal is to make these things 100% in America. We're going to have to build some machines in order to do this.
Your support is appreciated.

Mantle's 3D Printing for injection molds is a technology I'm very excited to explore. 
A huge thanks to Ted for participating!
Here's a video on what they do: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=uywWr6-nHF4

A HUGE thanks to our Injection Molder Chris Robson, with tons of work from Jeremy:
http://www.robsonco.com/

T&C Metal Stamping (Ask to speak to Weston and tell him Destin sent you!)
https://www.tandcstamping.com/

Search Engine Podcast: 
Episode "The Puzzle of the All-American BBQ Scrubber"
https://www.searchengine.show/the-puzzle-of-the-all-american-bbq-scrubber/

Check out Jeremy Fielding's Channel
https://www.youtube.com/@Jeremy_Fielding

Check out Tim Cook's comments on China at the Fortune Global Forum:
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=_ng8xQ-SNGc

~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
GET SMARTER SECTION

I recommend learning about the Bretton Woods Accords
https://www.federalreservehistory.org/essays/bretton-woods-created

Read about the Bretton Woods system
https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Bretton_Woods_system

~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~

Smarter Every Day on Patreon
http://www.patreon.com/smartereveryday

Ambiance, audio and musicy things by: Gordon McGladdery 
https://www.ashellinthepit.com/
http://ashellinthepit.bandcamp.com/

Warm Regards,

Destin

snippet.title: Los Angeles protests against ICE immigration raids continue; U.S. Marines, National Guard deployed
snippet.description:
More National Guard troops and hundreds of Marines have been deployed to Los Angeles as violent protests continued for another night, with more than 100 arrests Monday.

California Gov. Gavin Newsom continued to denounce sending the military into the city, filing an emergency motion to block the Marines' deployment. The National Guard has been protecting a federal complex in LA where some immigrants are being held after ICE raids around the city.

snippet.description:
Charity Lockhart’s journey from living in her car to taking the AGT stage is nothing short of inspiring. When her first song doesn’t land, she switches it up and impresses the judges with "Golden Slumbers" by The Beatles. Mel B can’t hold back her emotions, calling Charity “amazing” before slamming the Golden Buzzer!

snippet.title: ROG Xbox Ally World Premiere Reveal Trailer | Xbox Games Showcase
snippet.description:
Meet the ROG Xbox Ally and ROG Xbox Ally X. Coming this holiday 2025.

Introducing the ROG Xbox Ally and ROG Xbox Ally X – two new premium handhelds that combine the power of Xbox with the freedom of Windows 11. This holiday, players can discover another way to play as we combine the power of Xbox with the freedom you expect from Windows 11, created together with ASUS. And this is only the beginning.

•ROG Xbox Ally: powered by the AMD Ryzen™ Z2 A Processor - balancing performance and power consumption to maximize battery life without sacrificing gameplay quality - 16GB of RAM and 512GB of SSD storage.
•ROG Xbox Ally X: features the AMD Ryzen™ AI Z2 Extreme processor - allowing us to bring new experiences to life including greater frames-per-second, sharp visuals and increased intelligence - double the storage to have more native games at your fingertips, and 24GB of high-speed RAM and 1TB of SSD storage.

snippet.title: Just A Man | EPIC: The Musical Animatic
snippet.description:
Don't worry I kissed the brick before I threw it lol 
This one was a bummer BUT it was nice to do a shorter song. Before my comments are filled with "where is 600 strike" dont worry it is still being worked on I just want to do other things as well and not burn myself out!
I have a big merch drop coming to my shot in July and a  bunch of animatics/animation stories I want to tell

Music Credits to the very wicked ‪@JayHerrans  
(I don't own the rights to the song)

Song: Just A Man
Musical: Epic The Musical (Troy Saga)
Characters: Odysseus

snippet.title: LAPD chief speaks out about deployment of military forces to anti-ICE protests
snippet.description:
Los Angeles Police Department Chief Jim McDonnell and Los Angeles Mayor Karen Bass held a joint news conference Monday on the deployment of military forces to the city as protests over immigration raids continued. "I see two parallel tracks that don't work together, if you will," McDonnell said.

snippet.title: The Pickup - Official Trailer | Prime Video
snippet.description:
It’s pros vs cons. They’re armed but she’s dangerous. The Pickup premieres August 6.

In THE PICKUP, a routine cash pickup takes a wild turn when two mismatched armored truck drivers, RUSSELL (Eddie Murphy) and TRAVIS (Pete Davidson), are ambushed by ruthless criminals led by a savvy mastermind, ZOE (Keke Palmer), with plans that go way beyond the cash cargo. As chaos unfolds around them, the unlikely duo must navigate high-risk danger, clashing personalities, and one very bad day that keeps getting worse.

snippet.title: Four Days Later - Is the Switch 2 REALLY Worth $450?
snippet.description:
The Nintendo Switch 2 launched June 5, and now that the initial excitement and hype has died down, its time to review the unit. The Switch 2 represents an upgrade to the original Switch from 2017, but is it worth the $450 of your hard earned money? Lets dive in and take a closer look at the hardware.

TimeStamps:

00:00 - Intro
01:31 - Screen Brightness vs Switch OLED
02:36 - Setting up
03:10 - MicroSD Express and Game Key Cards
04:37 - Mario Kart World
06:11 - Fast Fusion & Cyberpunk 2077
08:23 - Back Compat with Switch 1
09:35 - Switch 2 Edition Updates
10:54 - Gamechat
13:10 - GameCube and N64 NSO
14:40 - Wi-Fi Speed Tests
16:03 - Thoughts/Conclusion

snippet.title: LIVE: BTS members JungKook and Jimin are discharged from South Korea military
